Thanks for downloading a copy of Modern Software Development Using Java.
We hope that you enjoy using this text as much as we enjoyed writing it.

There are two directories in this archive.  The directory "Text" cotains the
text in PDF form.  There is one file for each chapter in the book.  The
directory "Code" contains the code examples illustrated in the book.

We are distributing this text under the creative commons 
Attribution-Noncommercial-NoDerivs 3.0 Unported license.  The terms of this
license can be found in the file named LICENSE or by visiting the
creative commons web site.

